On check out there was a lovely woman who phoned for a taxi when we needed and they also let us leave our cases in the morning as we were not due to get our coach to the airport until 1pm.	Check out is 12pm but as our flight wasn't until 10pm they told us that we could leave the bags, use the pool and have a shower in the gym.	At 106 UK Pounds per night and based on previous Tripadvisor reviews, we felt that we had chosen a quality accommodation option by booking America Hotel for our first visit to Barcelona.